data.description: Immerse yourself in the vibrant Park Circle area, known for its thriving local businesses and welcoming community spirit!  Located just blocks from the brand new North Charleston community center and inclusive playground opening in November, this updated home has 2 bedrooms with a convenient jack and jill bath. Fenced yard with established trees and storage shed. New roof and water heater in 2021. Home could be for the first time homebuyer, rental investor, or downsizing owner ready to enjoy all that the Park Circle area has to offer!  Call for a showing today!
